      "title": "The annual Youth Activists for Abortion Access Summit is coming...",
      "content_html": "\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.18172-1/cp0/p50x50/21950661_1662566980443451_7358479861831904430_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103\u0026ccb=1-5\u0026_nc_sid=dbb9e7\u0026_nc_ohc=UiIsKtF5zOMAX94BsXs\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-1.fna\u0026oh=227acdd6bde33da7438f6cb8c432db98\u0026oe=614CD7A1\" alt=\"\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/\"\u003eACLU of Colorado\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/photos/a.131340536899444/4546719415361512/\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe annual Youth Activists for Abortion Access Summit is coming up on Saturday, September 11th. The summit will be a day of education, networking, and generally basking in the reproductive justice, health, and rights movement. The event is free and open to the public. RSVP at \u003ca href=\"http://yaaascolorado.org/rsvp\"\u003eyaaascolorado.org/rsvp\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NewEraColorado/\"\u003eNew Era Colorado\u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/S2SSisters/\"\u003eSoul 2 Soul Sisters\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/photos/a.131340536899444/4546719415361512/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/p526x296/240543113_4546719418694845_2047638465988660466_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104\u0026ccb=1-5\u0026_nc_sid=8024bb\u0026_nc_ohc=BPP-egEXqcUAX-o3Szc\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-2.fna\u0026oh=5332c520868896fa23ef759691535736\u0026oe=614B3BFF\" alt=\"May be a cartoon of text that says 'September 11, 2021 10am-4pm Denver, Co YAAAS! Join us for a day of education, networking, \u0026 generally basking in the glory of the reproductive justice, rights, \u0026 health movement! YOUTH ACTIVISTS FOR ABORTION ACCESS SUMMIT BRAZEN to save your spot, go to: yadascolorado.org/rsvp'\