l defense fund. For many, this is a cause for celebration, and the inspiration for events happening Saturday in Dura...\u003ca href=\"https://www.durangoherald.com/articles/legal-clinic-picnic-celebrate-creation-of-immigrant-legal-defense-fund/\"\u003eOn June 25, Gov. Jared Polis signed HB 1194 into law, establishing an immigrant legal defense fund. For many, this is a cause for celebration, and the inspiration for events happening Saturday in Dura...\u003c/a\u003e",
