      "title": "31 years after the passage of the Americans with Disabilities...",
      "content_html": "\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.18172-1/cp0/p50x50/21950661_1662566980443451_7358479861831904430_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103\u0026ccb=1-5\u0026_nc_sid=dbb9e7\u0026_nc_ohc=UiIsKtF5zOMAX94BsXs\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-1.fna\u0026oh=227acdd6bde33da7438f6cb8c432db98\u0026oe=614CD7A1\" alt=\"\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/\"\u003eACLU of Colorado\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/photos/a.131340536899444/4459825487384239/\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003cp\u003e31 years after the passage of the Americans with Disabilities Act, over 800,000 people with disabilities are on waiting lists for home care services. Even more are entering institutions against their wishes because they do not have enough direct care staff to support them at home. Learn more about how to change this. RSVP: \u003ca href=\"https://go.peoplepower.org/event/action/23231\"\u003ehttps://go.peoplepower.org/event/action/23231\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/acluofcolorado/photos/a.131340536899444/4459825487384239/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/s526x296/224919908_4459825497384238_1544347890844303652_n.jpg?_nc_cat=101\u0026ccb=1-5\u0026_nc_sid=8024bb\u0026_nc_ohc=hNbqUPJMReYAX9nj6cc\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-1.fna\u0026oh=9b46ba7541911ce1a025c3585e6f83c3\u0026oe=614C1629\" alt=\"May be an image of text that says 'ACLU THE BETTER CARE BETTER JOBS ACT and the Disability Community Webinar on Wednesday, July 28, 6 p.m.'\" width=\"500\" height=\"262\" caption=\"May be an image of text that says 'ACLU THE BETTER CARE BETTER JOBS ACT and the Disability Community Webinar on Wednesday, July 28, 6 p.m.'\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e",
